# Introduction to Amazon RDS

Amazon RDS is AWS managed relational database service.

Purpose of RDS:
- Database hosting
- Database management
- Automated backups
- Scalable database infrastructure

Supported database engines include:
- MySQL
- PostgreSQL
- MariaDB
- Oracle
- SQL Server

